When you enter the Dimensional Rift, you'll arrive in the Outer Realm (虚域). This dimension is extremely dark, so make sure to prepare Night Vision Potions and Torches to help you navigate.

Important Preparations:
Night Vision Potions:
The Outer Realm is very dim, and it's easy to get lost without proper lighting. Carry plenty of Night Vision Potions to make it easier to see in the dark.

Torches:
As a backup, bring Torches to light your surroundings. While Night Vision is great, torches will help you mark your path and keep some areas well-lit.

Watch for the Void:
The Outer Realm has dangerous voids scattered throughout. Be careful not to fall into these abysses as it can be deadly. Stay aware of where you're walking.

Warning:
